        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued April 4 at 12:33AM CDT until April 4 at 1:30AM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>SVRMAF

The National Weather Service in Midland has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Southeastern Glasscock County in western Texas...
Northwestern Reagan County in western Texas...

* Until 130 AM CDT.

* At 1233 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 13 miles
northwest of Reagan County Airport, or 14 miles northwest of Big
Lake, moving northeast at 40 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles.

* Locations impacted include...
Stiles.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
